These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
City: berlin, rome
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| City   | rome  | berlin |
| Birthday       | june | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, bike
2 different games are played: snooker, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
2. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Transport   | motorbike | bike |
| Game      | whist     | snooker  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, jet-ski
There 2 different types of food: apricot, pepper
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Transport   | van | jet-ski  |
| Food   | apricot | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
House: tower, victorian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| House   | victorian | tower   |
| Flower       | bellflower | poppy |

