The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Beverage   | water    | cola    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | family |

