1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Flower   | orchid | aconite |
| Pet     | frog        | snake |

