City: london, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | old-henry |
| City     | london | marseilles    |

